msgstr "默认值： ``False``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:258
msgid ""
"If enabled, Scrapy will log all cookies sent in requests (i.e. ``Cookie`` "
"header) and all cookies received in responses (i.e. ``Set-Cookie`` header)."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，Scrapy 将记录在请求中发送的所有 cookie (例如``Cookie`` 头)和在响应"
"中收到的所有 cookie (例如``Set-Cookie`` 头)。"

