#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:275
msgid "DefaultHeadersMiddleware"
msgstr "默认Headers中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:282
msgid ""
"This middleware sets all default requests headers specified in the :setting:"
"`DEFAULT_REQUEST_HEADERS` setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:286
msgid "DownloadTimeoutMiddleware"
msgstr "下载超时中件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:293
msgid ""
"This middleware sets the download timeout for requests specified in the :"
"setting:`DOWNLOAD_TIMEOUT` setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:298
msgid ""
"You can also set download timeout per-request using the :reqmeta:"
"`download_timeout` :attr:`.Request.meta` key; this is supported even when "
"DownloadTimeoutMiddleware is disabled."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:303
msgid "HttpAuthMiddleware"
msgstr "HttpAuthMiddleware"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:310
msgid ""
"This middleware authenticates all requests generated from certain spiders "
"using `Basic access authentication`_ (aka. HTTP auth)."
msgstr ""
"此中间件使用 `Basic Access authentication`_ (aka. HTTP auth) 验证某些特定间谍"
"生成的所有请求。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:313
msgid ""
"To enable HTTP authentication for a spider, set the ``http_user`` and "
"``http_pass`` spider attributes to the authentication data and the "
"``http_auth_domain`` spider attribute to the domain which requires this "
"authentication (its subdomains will be also handled in the same way). You "
"can set ``http_auth_domain`` to ``None`` to enable the authentication for "
"all requests but you risk leaking your authentication credentials to "
"unrelated domains."
msgstr ""
"为蜘蛛启用 HTTP 身份验证， 将 ``http_user`` 和 ``http_pass`` 的 spider 属性设"
"置为认证数据和 ``http_auth_domain`` 的 spider 属性设置为需要此身份验证的域(其"
"子域也将以同样的方式处理)。 你可以将 ``http_auth_domain`` 设置为 ``None`` 以"
"启用所有请求的身份验证，但是你可能会将你的身份验证证书泄漏到无关的域。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:322
msgid ""
"In previous Scrapy versions HttpAuthMiddleware sent the authentication data "
"with all requests, which is a security problem if the spider makes requests "
"to several different domains. Currently if the ``http_auth_domain`` "
"attribute is not set, the middleware will use the domain of the first "
"request, which will work for some spiders but not for others. In the future "
"the middleware will produce an error instead."
msgstr ""
"在以前的 Scrapy 版本中，HttpAuthMiddleware 发送了所有请求的身份验证数据。 如"
"果蜘蛛对几个不同的域提出请求，那将是一个安全问题。 目前如果"
"``http_auth_domain`` 属性未设定。 中间件将使用第一个请求的域，这个域将适用于"
"某些间谍，但不适用于另一些间谍。 今后，中间件将产生错误。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:329
#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:429
msgid "Example:"
msgstr "示例："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:331
msgid ""
"from scrapy.spiders import CrawlSpider\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"class SomeIntranetSiteSpider(CrawlSpider):\n"
"    http_user = \"someuser\"\n"
"    http_pass = \"somepass\"\n"
"    http_auth_domain = \"intranet.example.com\"\n"
"    name = \"intranet.example.com\"\n"
"\n"
"    # .. rest of the spider code omitted ..."
msgstr ""
"来自废料。 piders importer CrawlSpider\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"class IntranetSiteSpider(CrawlSpider):\n"
"    http_user = \"somepass\"\n"
"    http_pass= \"somepass\"\n"
"    http_auth_domain = \"intrannet. xample.com\"\n"
"    name = \"intranet.example.com\"\n"
"\n"
"    # ... 剩余的 spider 代码省略..."

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:348
msgid "HttpCacheMiddleware"
msgstr "HttpCache中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:355
msgid ""
"This middleware provides low-level cache to all HTTP requests and responses. "
"It has to be combined with a cache storage backend as well as a cache policy."
msgstr ""
"这个中间件为所有HTTP请求和响应提供低级缓存。 它必须与缓存存储后端和缓存策略相"
"结合。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:358
msgid "Scrapy ships with the following HTTP cache storage backends:"
msgstr "废料带有以下HTTP缓存存储后端："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:360
msgid ":ref:`httpcache-storage-fs`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:361
msgid ":ref:`httpcache-storage-dbm`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:363
msgid ""
"You can change the HTTP cache storage backend with the :setting:"
"`HTTPCACHE_STORAGE` setting. Or you can also :ref:`implement your own "
"storage backend. <httpcache-storage-custom>`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:366
msgid "Scrapy ships with two HTTP cache policies:"
msgstr "带有两个HTTP缓存策略的废船："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:368
msgid ":ref:`httpcache-policy-rfc2616`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:369
msgid ":ref:`httpcache-policy-dummy`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:371
msgid ""
"You can change the HTTP cache policy with the :setting:`HTTPCACHE_POLICY` "
"setting. Or you can also implement your own policy."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:376
msgid ""
"You can also avoid caching a response on every policy using :reqmeta:"
"`dont_cache` meta key equals ``True``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:384
msgid "Dummy policy (default)"
msgstr "虚拟策略 (默认)"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:388
msgid ""
"This policy has no awareness of any HTTP Cache-Control directives. Every "
"request and its corresponding response are cached.  When the same request is "
"seen again, the response is returned without transferring anything from the "
"Internet."
msgstr ""
"此策略不知道任何 HTTP 缓存控制指令。每个请求及其相应响应都是缓存的。 当再次看"
"到同样的请求时，将在没有从因特网上转移任何东西的情况下回来答复。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:393
msgid ""
"The Dummy policy is useful for testing spiders faster (without having to "
"wait for downloads every time) and for trying your spider offline, when an "
"Internet connection is not available. The goal is to be able to \"replay\" a "
"spider run *exactly as it ran before*."
msgstr ""
"虚拟策略有助于更快地测试蜘蛛(无需每次等待下载)和尝试你的蜘蛛脱机。 当互联网连"
"接不可用。 目标是能够“重放”一个蜘蛛运行*就像它之前运行的那样*。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:402
msgid "RFC2616 policy"
msgstr "RFC2616政策"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:406
msgid ""
"This policy provides a RFC2616 compliant HTTP cache, i.e. with HTTP Cache-"
"Control awareness, aimed at production and used in continuous runs to avoid "
"downloading unmodified data (to save bandwidth and speed up crawls)."
msgstr ""
"此策略提供 RFC2616 兼容的 HTTP 缓存，即： 使用 HTTP Cache-Control 意识，旨在"
"生产并用于连续运行，以避免下载未经修改的数据(以节省带宽和加速crawls)。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:411
msgid "What is implemented:"
msgstr "已经执行的任务："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:413
msgid ""
"Do not attempt to store responses/requests with ``no-store`` cache-control "
"directive set"
msgstr "不要尝试使用 ``no-store`` 缓存控制指令设置存储响应/请求"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:414
msgid ""
"Do not serve responses from cache if ``no-cache`` cache-control directive is "
"set even for fresh responses"
msgstr ""
"如果设置了 ``no-cache`` 缓存控制指令，即使是新的响应，请不要为缓存响应服务。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:415
msgid "Compute freshness lifetime from ``max-age`` cache-control directive"
msgstr "从 ``max-age`` 缓存控制指令计算淡化生命期"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:416
msgid "Compute freshness lifetime from ``Expires`` response header"
msgstr "计算从 ``Expires`` 响应头的淡化生存期"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:417
msgid ""
"Compute freshness lifetime from ``Last-Modified`` response header (heuristic "
"used by Firefox)"
msgstr "从 ``Last-Modified`` 响应头计算淡化生命周期(Firefox使用的heuristic"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:418
msgid "Compute current age from ``Age`` response header"
msgstr "从 ``Age`` 响应头计算当前年龄"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:419
msgid "Compute current age from ``Date`` header"
msgstr "从 ``Date`` 头计算当前年龄"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:420
msgid "Revalidate stale responses based on ``Last-Modified`` response header"
msgstr "基于``Last-Modified`` 响应头的无效响应"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:421
msgid "Revalidate stale responses based on ``ETag`` response header"
msgstr "基于``ETag`` 响应头的更新过时响应"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:422
msgid "Set ``Date`` header for any received response missing it"
msgstr "设置 ``Date`` 标头缺少任何接收到的响应"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:423
msgid "Support ``max-stale`` cache-control directive in requests"
msgstr "在请求中支持 ``max-stale`` 缓存控制指令"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:425
msgid ""
"This allows spiders to be configured with the full RFC2616 cache policy, but "
"avoid revalidation on a request-by-request basis, while remaining conformant "
"with the HTTP spec."
msgstr ""
"这将允许使用完整的 RFC2616 缓存策略配置蜘蛛。 但避免在请求基础上重新验证，同"
"时仍然符合HTTP投机。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:431
msgid ""
"Add ``Cache-Control: max-stale=600`` to Request headers to accept responses "
"that have exceeded their expiration time by no more than 600 seconds."
msgstr ""
"添加 ``Cache-Control: max-stale=600`` 以请求头部接受超过到期时间不超过 600 秒"
"的答复。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:434
msgid "See also: RFC2616, 14.9.3"
msgstr "另见：RFC2616，14.9.3"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:436
msgid "What is missing:"
msgstr "缺失的内容："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:438
msgid ""
"``Pragma: no-cache`` support https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-"
"sec14.html#sec14.9.1"
msgstr ""
"``Pragma: no-cache`` 支持 https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec14."
"html#sec14.9.1"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:439
msgid ""
"``Vary`` header support https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec13."
"html#sec13.6"
msgstr ""
"``Vary`` header 支持 https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec13."
"html#sec13.6"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:440
msgid ""
"Invalidation after updates or deletes https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/"
"rfc2616-sec13.html#sec13.10"
msgstr ""
"更新后无效或删除https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec13."
"html#sec13.10"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:441
msgid "... probably others .."
msgstr "... 可能是其他..."

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:447
msgid "Filesystem storage backend (default)"
msgstr "文件系统存储后端 (默认)"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:451
msgid "File system storage backend is available for the HTTP cache middleware."
msgstr "文件系统存储后端可用于 HTTP 缓存中间件。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:453
msgid ""
"Each request/response pair is stored in a different directory containing the "
"following files:"
msgstr "每对请求/响应都存储在不同的目录中，包含以下文件："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:456
msgid "``request_body`` - the plain request body"
msgstr "``request_body`` - 纯请求体"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:458
msgid "``request_headers`` - the request headers (in raw HTTP format)"
msgstr "``request_headers`` - 请求标题(原HTTP格式)"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:460
msgid "``response_body`` - the plain response body"
msgstr "``response_body`` - 纯响应体"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:462
msgid "``response_headers`` - the request headers (in raw HTTP format)"
msgstr "``response_headers`` - 请求标题(原HTTP格式)"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:464
msgid ""
"``meta`` - some metadata of this cache resource in Python ``repr()`` format "
"(grep-friendly format)"
msgstr ""
"``meta`` - 此缓存资源的一些元数据为 Python ``repr()`` 格式 (grep-friendly 格"
"式)"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:467
msgid ""
"``pickled_meta`` - the same metadata in ``meta`` but pickled for more "
"efficient deserialization"
msgstr "``picked_meta`` - ``meta`` 中相同的元数据，但是为了更有效的反序列化"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:470
msgid ""
"The directory name is made from the request fingerprint (see ``scrapy.utils."
"request.fingerprint``), and one level of subdirectories is used to avoid "
"creating too many files into the same directory (which is inefficient in "
"many file systems). An example directory could be::"
msgstr ""
"目录名称来自请求指纹(见``scrapy.utils.request)。 cinerprint``，一个层次的子目"
"录被用来避免将太多的文件创建到同一个目录中(在许多文件系统中效率不高)。 一个示"
"例目录可以是:"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:475
msgid ""
"/path/to/cache/dir/example.com/72/72811f648e718090f041317756c03adb0ada46c7"
msgstr ""
"/path/to/cache/dir/example.com/72/72811f648e718090f041317756c03adb0ada46c7"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:480
msgid "DBM storage backend"
msgstr "DBM 存储后端"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:484
msgid "A DBM_ storage backend is also available for the HTTP cache middleware."
msgstr "一个 DBM_ 存储后端也可用于 HTTP 缓存中级设备。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:486
msgid ""
"By default, it uses the :mod:`dbm`, but you can change it with the :setting:"
"`HTTPCACHE_DBM_MODULE` setting."
