#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:546
msgid "HTTPCache middleware settings"
msgstr "HTTPache 中间件设置"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:548
msgid ""
"The :class:`HttpCacheMiddleware` can be configured through the following "
"settings:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:554
msgid "HTTPCACHE_ENABLED"
msgstr "HTTPCACHE_已启用"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:558
msgid "Whether the HTTP cache will be enabled."
msgstr "是否启用 HTTP 缓存。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:563
msgid "HTTPCACHE_EXPIRATION_SECS"
msgstr "HTTPHE_EXPIRATION_SECS"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:565
msgid "Default: ``0``"
msgstr "默认值: ``0``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:567
msgid "Expiration time for cached requests, in seconds."
msgstr "缓存请求的过期时间，以秒计。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:569
msgid ""
"Cached requests older than this time will be re-downloaded. If zero, cached "
"requests will never expire."
msgstr "超过此时间的缓存请求将被重新下载。如果为零，缓存请求将永远不会过期。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:575
msgid "HTTPCACHE_DIR"
msgstr "HTTPCACHE_DIR"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:577
msgid "Default: ``'httpcache'``"
msgstr "Default: ``'httpcache'``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:579
msgid ""
"The directory to use for storing the (low-level) HTTP cache. If empty, the "
"HTTP cache will be disabled. If a relative path is given, is taken relative "
"to the project data dir. For more info see: :ref:`topics-project-structure`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:586
msgid "HTTPCACHE_IGNORE_HTTP_CODES"
msgstr "HTTPHE_IGNORE_HTTP_CODES"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:588
#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:671
#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:935
msgid "Default: ``[]``"
msgstr "默认值： ``[]``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:590
msgid "Don't cache response with these HTTP codes."
msgstr "不要缓存这些HTTP代码的响应。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:595
msgid "HTTPCACHE_IGNORE_MISSING"
msgstr "HTTPHE_IGNORE_MISSSING"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:599
msgid ""
"If enabled, requests not found in the cache will be ignored instead of "
"downloaded."
msgstr "如果启用，缓存中找不到的请求将被忽略而不是下载。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:604
msgid "HTTPCACHE_IGNORE_SCHEMES"
msgstr "HTTPCACHE_IGNORE_SCHEMES"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:606
msgid "Default: ``['file']``"
msgstr "默认值： ``['file']``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:608
msgid "Don't cache responses with these URI schemes."
msgstr "不要缓存这些URI方案的回复。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:613
msgid "HTTPCACHE_STORAGE"
msgstr "HTTPHE_STORAGE_TITLE"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:615
msgid "Default: ``'scrapy.extensions.httpcache.FilesystemCacheStorage'``"
msgstr "默认值： ``'scrapy.extensions.httpcache.filesystemCacheStorage'``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:617
msgid "The class which implements the cache storage backend."
msgstr "该类实现缓存存储后端。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:622
msgid "HTTPCACHE_DBM_MODULE"
msgstr "HTTPCACHE_DBM_MODULE"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:624
msgid "Default: ``'dbm'``"
msgstr "Default: ``'dbm'``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:626
msgid ""
"The database module to use in the :ref:`DBM storage backend <httpcache-"
"storage-dbm>`. This setting is specific to the DBM backend."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:632
msgid "HTTPCACHE_POLICY"
msgstr "HTTPHE_POLICY"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:634
msgid "Default: ``'scrapy.extensions.httpcache.DummyPolicy'``"
msgstr "默认： ``'scrapy.extensions.httpcache.DummyPolicy'``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:636
msgid "The class which implements the cache policy."
msgstr "执行缓存策略的类。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:641
msgid "HTTPCACHE_GZIP"
msgstr "HTTPHE_GZIP"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:645
msgid ""
"If enabled, will compress all cached data with gzip. This setting is "
"specific to the Filesystem backend."
msgstr "如果启用，将所有缓存数据以 gzip压缩。此设置是专门针对文件系统后端的。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:651
msgid "HTTPCACHE_ALWAYS_STORE"
msgstr "HTTPHE_ALWAYS_STORE"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:655
msgid "If enabled, will cache pages unconditionally."
msgstr "如果启用，将无条件缓存页面。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:657
msgid ""
"A spider may wish to have all responses available in the cache, for future "
"use with ``Cache-Control: max-stale``, for instance. The DummyPolicy caches "
"all responses but never revalidates them, and sometimes a more nuanced "
"policy is desirable."
msgstr ""
"一个蜘蛛可能希望在缓存中提供所有的响应，供将来使用 ``Cache-Control：max-"
"stale`` 。 DummyPolicy 缓存所有响应，但永远不会重新验证它们，有时需要更细致的"
"政策。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:662
msgid ""
"This setting still respects ``Cache-Control: no-store`` directives in "
"responses. If you don't want that, filter ``no-store`` out of the Cache-"
"Control headers in responses you feed to the cache middleware."
msgstr ""
"此设置仍然遵守响应中的 ``Cache-Control: no-store`` 指令。 如果你不想这样做，"
"在你给缓存中期的回复中，过滤器``no-store`` 。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:669
msgid "HTTPCACHE_IGNORE_RESPONSE_CACHE_CONTROLS"
msgstr "HTTPCACHE_IGNORE_RESPONSE_CACHE_CONTROLS"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:673
msgid "List of Cache-Control directives in responses to be ignored."
msgstr "响应中的 Cache-Control 指令列表被忽略。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:675
msgid ""
"Sites often set \"no-store\", \"no-cache\", \"must-revalidate\", etc., but "
"get upset at the traffic a spider can generate if it actually respects those "
"directives. This allows to selectively ignore Cache-Control directives that "
"are known to be unimportant for the sites being crawled."
msgstr ""
"站点常常设置“无商店”、“无缓存”、“必须重新验证”等，但如果一个蜘蛛实际遵守这些"
"指令，就会对其生成的流量感到失望。 这允许有选择地忽略已知对被夷为平地站点不重"
"要的缓存控制指令。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:680
msgid ""
"We assume that the spider will not issue Cache-Control directives in "
"requests unless it actually needs them, so directives in requests are not "
"filtered."
msgstr ""
"我们假设，除非执行者实际需要，在请求中不会发布缓存控制指令，因此请求中的指令"
"不会被过滤。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:685
msgid "HttpCompressionMiddleware"
msgstr "HttpComppression中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:692
msgid ""
"This middleware allows compressed (gzip, deflate) traffic to be sent/"
"received from web sites."
msgstr "这个中间件允许从网站发送/接收压缩的 (gzip、调制) 流量。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:695
msgid ""
"This middleware also supports decoding `brotli-compressed`_ as well as `zstd-"
"compressed`_ responses, provided that `brotli`_ or `zstandard`_ is "
"installed, respectively."
msgstr ""
"这个中间件还支持解码 `brotli-compressed`_ 和 `zstd-compressed`_ 反应，但条件"
"是必须安装`brotli`_ 或 `zstandard`_ 。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:706
msgid "HttpCompressionMiddleware Settings"
msgstr "HttpComppression中间件设置"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:711
msgid "COMPRESSION_ENABLED"
msgstr "开启_EMAT"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:715
msgid "Whether the Compression middleware will be enabled."
msgstr "是否启用压缩中间件功能。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:719
msgid "HttpProxyMiddleware"
msgstr "HttpProxyMiddleware"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:728
msgid ""
"This middleware sets the HTTP proxy to use for requests, by setting the :"
"reqmeta:`proxy` meta value for :class:`~scrapy.Request` objects."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:731
msgid ""
"Like the Python standard library module :mod:`urllib.request`, it obeys the "
"following environment variables:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:734
msgid "``http_proxy``"
msgstr "``http_proxy``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:735
msgid "``https_proxy``"
msgstr "``https://_proxy``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:736
msgid "``no_proxy``"
msgstr "``no_proxy``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:738
msgid ""
"You can also set the meta key :reqmeta:`proxy` per-request, to a value like "
"``http://some_proxy_server:port`` or ``http://username:"
"password@some_proxy_server:port``. Keep in mind this value will take "
"precedence over ``http_proxy``/``https_proxy`` environment variables, and it "
"will also ignore ``no_proxy`` environment variable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:745
msgid ""
"Handling of this meta key needs to be implemented inside the :ref:`download "
"handler <topics-download-handlers>`, so it's not guaranteed to be supported "
"by all 3rd-party handlers. It's currently unsupported by :class:`~scrapy."
"core.downloader.handlers.http2.H2DownloadHandler` and :class:`~scrapy.core."
"downloader.handlers._httpx.HttpxDownloadHandler`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:753
msgid ""
"Usually a proxy URL uses the ``http://`` scheme. More rarely, it uses the "
"``https://`` one. While both kinds of proxy URLs can be used with both HTTP "
"and HTTPS destination URLs, the specifics of the network exchange are "
"different for all 4 cases and it's possible that HTTPS proxies are fully or "
"partially unsupported by a given download handler. Currently, :class:"
"`~scrapy.core.downloader.handlers.http11.HTTP11DownloadHandler` supports "
"HTTPS proxies only for HTTP destinations."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:762
msgid "HttpProxyMiddleware settings"
msgstr "HttpProxyMiddleware 设置"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:768
msgid "HTTPPROXY_ENABLED"
msgstr "HTTPPROXY_已启用"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:772
msgid "Whether or not to enable the :class:`HttpProxyMiddleware`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:775
msgid "HTTPPROXY_AUTH_ENCODING"
msgstr "HTTPPROXY_AUTH_ENCODE"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:777
msgid "Default: ``\"latin-1\"``"
msgstr "默认： ``\"latin-1\"``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:779
msgid ""
"The default encoding for proxy authentication on :class:"
"`HttpProxyMiddleware`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:782
msgid "OffsiteMiddleware"
msgstr "离站中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:791
msgid ""
"Filters out Requests for URLs outside the domains covered by the spider."
msgstr "过滤超越拼写器覆盖域外的 URL 请求。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:793
msgid ""
"This middleware filters out every request whose host names aren't in the "
"spider's :attr:`~scrapy.Spider.allowed_domains` attribute. All subdomains of "
"any domain in the list are also allowed. E.g. the rule ``www.example.org`` "
"will also allow ``bob.www.example.org`` but not ``www2.example.com`` nor "
"``example.com``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:799
msgid ""
"When your spider returns a request for a domain not belonging to those "
"covered by the spider, this middleware will log a debug message similar to "
"this one::"
msgstr ""
"当你的蜘蛛返回一个不属于蜘蛛所覆盖的域的请求时， 这个中间件将记录一个与此相似"
"的调试消息："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:803
msgid ""
"DEBUG: Filtered offsite request to 'offsite.example': <GET http://offsite."
"example/some/page.html>"
msgstr ""
"DEBUG: 已过滤的离站请求为“offsite.example”: <GET http://offsite.example/some/"
"page.html>"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:805
msgid ""
"To avoid filling the log with too much noise, it will only print one of "
"these messages for each new domain filtered. So, for example, if another "
"request for ``offsite.example`` is filtered, no log message will be printed. "
"But if a request for ``other.example`` is filtered, a message will be "
"printed (but only for the first request filtered)."
msgstr ""
"为了避免用太多的噪声填充日志，它只能打印每个新域过滤中的一条消息。 例如，如果"
"有另一个请求“离站”。 xample`` 被过滤，将不会打印日志消息。但是如果请求“其"
"他”。 xample`` 已被过滤，消息将被打印(但只适用于第一次请求过滤)。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:811
msgid ""
"If the spider doesn't define an :attr:`~scrapy.Spider.allowed_domains` "
"attribute, or the attribute is empty, the offsite middleware will allow all "
"requests."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:817
msgid ""
"If the request has the :attr:`~scrapy.Request.dont_filter` attribute set to "
"``True`` or :attr:`Request.meta` has ``allow_offsite`` set to ``True``, then "
"the OffsiteMiddleware will allow the request even if its domain is not "
"listed in allowed domains."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:823
msgid "RedirectMiddleware"
msgstr "重定向中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:830
msgid ""
"This middleware handles redirection of requests based on response status."
msgstr "这个中间件处理基于响应状态的请求重定向。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:834
msgid ""
"The urls which the request goes through (while being redirected) can be "
"found in the ``redirect_urls`` :attr:`Request.meta <scrapy.Request.meta>` "
"key."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:839
msgid ""
"The reason behind each redirect in :reqmeta:`redirect_urls` can be found in "
"the ``redirect_reasons`` :attr:`Request.meta <scrapy.Request.meta>` key. For "
"example: ``[301, 302, 307, 'meta refresh']``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:843
msgid ""
"The format of a reason depends on the middleware that handled the "
"corresponding redirect. For example, :class:`RedirectMiddleware` indicates "
"the triggering response status code as an integer, while :class:"
"`MetaRefreshMiddleware` always uses the ``'meta refresh'`` string as reason."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:848
msgid ""
"The :class:`RedirectMiddleware` can be configured through the following "
"settings (see the settings documentation for more info):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:851
msgid ":setting:`REDIRECT_ENABLED`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:852
msgid ":setting:`REDIRECT_MAX_TIMES`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:856
msgid ""
"If :attr:`Request.meta <scrapy.Request.meta>` has ``dont_redirect`` key set "
"to True, the request will be ignored by this middleware."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:859
msgid ""
"If you want to handle some redirect status codes in your spider, you can "
"specify these in the ``handle_httpstatus_list`` spider attribute."
msgstr ""
"如果你想要处理你的蜘蛛中的一些重定向状态代码，你可以在 "
"``handle_httpstatus_list`` 的属性中指定这些代码。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:862
msgid ""
"For example, if you want the redirect middleware to ignore 301 and 302 "
"responses (and pass them through to your spider) you can do this:"
msgstr ""
"例如，如果你想要重定向中间件忽略301和302反应(并将它们传递给你的蜘蛛)，你可以"
"这样做："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:865
msgid ""
"class MySpider(CrawlSpider):\n"
"    handle_httpstatus_list = [301, 302]"
msgstr ""
"MySpider(CrawlSpider):\n"
"    handle_httpstatus_list = [301, 302]"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:870
msgid ""
"The ``handle_httpstatus_list`` key of :attr:`Request.meta <scrapy.Request."
"meta>` can also be used to specify which response codes to allow on a per-"
"request basis. You can also set the meta key ``handle_httpstatus_all`` to "
"``True`` if you want to allow any response code for a request."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:878
msgid "RedirectMiddleware settings"
msgstr "重定向中间件设置"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:883
msgid "REDIRECT_ENABLED"
msgstr "REDIRECT_已启用"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:887
msgid "Whether the Redirect middleware will be enabled."
msgstr "是否启用重定向中间件."

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:892
msgid "REDIRECT_MAX_TIMES"
msgstr "REDIRECT_MAX_TIMES"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:894
msgid "Default: ``20``"
msgstr "默认值： ``20``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:896
msgid ""
"The maximum number of redirections that will be followed for a single "
"request. If maximum redirections are exceeded, the request is aborted and "
"ignored."
msgstr ""
"单个请求所遵循的最大重定向次数。如果超过最大重定向，请求将被中止和忽略。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:900
msgid "MetaRefreshMiddleware"
msgstr "元刷新中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:904
msgid ""
"This middleware handles redirection of requests based on meta-refresh html "
"tag."
msgstr "此中间件处理基于元刷新html 标签的请求重定向。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:906
msgid ""
"The :class:`MetaRefreshMiddleware` can be configured through the following "
"settings (see the settings documentation for more info):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:909
msgid ":setting:`METAREFRESH_ENABLED`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:910
msgid ":setting:`METAREFRESH_IGNORE_TAGS`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:911
msgid ":setting:`METAREFRESH_MAXDELAY`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:913
msgid ""
"This middleware obey :setting:`REDIRECT_MAX_TIMES` setting, :reqmeta:"
"`dont_redirect`, :reqmeta:`redirect_urls` and :reqmeta:`redirect_reasons` "
"request meta keys as described for :class:`RedirectMiddleware`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:919
msgid "MetaRefreshMiddleware settings"
msgstr "元刷新中间件设置"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:924
msgid "METAREFRESH_ENABLED"
msgstr "METAREFRESH_PLAYLIN"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:928
msgid "Whether the Meta Refresh middleware will be enabled."
msgstr "Meta 刷新中间件是否启用。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:933
msgid "METAREFRESH_IGNORE_TAGS"
msgstr "METAREFRESH_INTERNATIONAL"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:937
msgid "Meta tags within these tags are ignored."
msgstr "忽略这些标签中的元标签。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:939
msgid ""
"The default value of :setting:`METAREFRESH_IGNORE_TAGS` changed from ``[]`` "
"to ``[\"noscript\"]``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:946
msgid "METAREFRESH_MAXDELAY"
msgstr "METAREFRESH_MEXDELAY"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:948
msgid "Default: ``100``"
msgstr "默认值： ``100``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:950
msgid ""
"The maximum meta-refresh delay (in seconds) to follow the redirection. Some "
"sites use meta-refresh for redirecting to a session expired page, so we "
"restrict automatic redirection to the maximum delay."
msgstr ""
"最大元刷新延迟(以秒为单位)以跟随重定向。 有些站点使用元刷新来重定向到会话过期"
"页面，所以我们限制自动重定向到最大延迟。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:955
msgid "RetryMiddleware"
msgstr "重试中间件"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:962
msgid ""
"A middleware to retry failed requests that are potentially caused by "
"temporary problems such as a connection timeout or HTTP 500 error."
msgstr "重试失败请求的中间件，如连接超时或 HTTP 500 错误。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:965
msgid ""
"Failed pages are collected on the scraping process and rescheduled at the "
"end, once the spider has finished crawling all regular (non failed) pages."
msgstr ""
"在拆解过程中收集失败的页面，并在结束时重新安排时间，一旦旋转器完成整理所有常"
"规(非失败)页面。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:968
msgid ""
"The :class:`RetryMiddleware` can be configured through the following "
"settings (see the settings documentation for more info):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:971
msgid ":setting:`RETRY_ENABLED`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:972
msgid ":setting:`RETRY_TIMES`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:973
msgid ":setting:`RETRY_HTTP_CODES`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:974
msgid ":setting:`RETRY_EXCEPTIONS`"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:978
msgid ""
"If :attr:`Request.meta <scrapy.Request.meta>` has ``dont_retry`` key set to "
"True, the request will be ignored by this middleware."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:981
msgid ""
"To retry requests from a spider callback, you can use the :func:"
"`get_retry_request` function:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:1
msgid ""
"Returns a new :class:`~scrapy.Request` object to retry the specified "
"request, or ``None`` if retries of the specified request have been exhausted."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:5
msgid ""
"For example, in a :class:`~scrapy.Spider` callback, you could use it as "
"follows::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:8
msgid ""
"def parse(self, response):\n"
"    if not response.text:\n"
"        new_request_or_none = get_retry_request(\n"
"            response.request,\n"
"            spider=self,\n"
"            reason='empty',\n"
"        )\n"
"        return new_request_or_none"
msgstr ""
"def parse(self, response):\n"
"    if not response.text:\n"
"        new_request_or_none = get_retry_request(\n"
"            response.request,\n"
"            spider=self,\n"
"            reason='empty',\n"
"        )\n"
"        return new_request_or_no"

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:17
msgid ""
"*spider* is the :class:`~scrapy.Spider` instance which is asking for the "
"retry request. It is used to access the :ref:`settings <topics-settings>` "
"and :ref:`stats <topics-stats>`, and to provide extra logging context (see :"
"func:`logging.debug`)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:22
msgid ""
"*reason* is a string or an :class:`Exception` object that indicates the "
"reason why the request needs to be retried. It is used to name retry stats."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:25
msgid ""
"*max_retry_times* is a number that determines the maximum number of times "
"that *request* can be retried. If not specified or ``None``, the number is "
"read from the :reqmeta:`max_retry_times` meta key of the request. If the :"
"reqmeta:`max_retry_times` meta key is not defined or ``None``, the number is "
"read from the :setting:`RETRY_TIMES` setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:31
msgid ""
"*priority_adjust* is a number that determines how the priority of the new "
"request changes in relation to *request*. If not specified, the number is "
"read from the :setting:`RETRY_PRIORITY_ADJUST` setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:35
msgid "*logger* is the logging.Logger object to be used when logging messages"
msgstr "*logger* 是日志记录器对象将在记录消息时使用"

#: ../../../../scrapy/downloadermiddlewares/retry.py:docstring of
#: scrapy.downloadermiddlewares.retry.get_retry_request:37
msgid ""
"*stats_base_key* is a string to be used as the base key for the retry-"
"related job stats"
msgstr "*stats_base_key* 是一个字符串，可用作与重试相关的作业统计的基本密钥"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:987
msgid "RetryMiddleware Settings"
msgstr "RetryMiddleware 设置"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:992
msgid "RETRY_ENABLED"
msgstr "RETRY_已启用"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:996
msgid "Whether the Retry middleware will be enabled."
msgstr "是否启用重试中间件."

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1001
msgid "RETRY_TIMES"
msgstr "TRY_TIMES"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1003
msgid "Default: ``2``"
msgstr "默认: ``2``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1005
msgid "Maximum number of times to retry, in addition to the first download."
msgstr "除第一次下载外，重试的最大次数。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1007
msgid ""
"Maximum number of retries can also be specified per-request using :reqmeta:"
"`max_retry_times` attribute of :attr:`Request.meta <scrapy.Request.meta>`. "
"When initialized, the :reqmeta:`max_retry_times` meta key takes higher "
"precedence over the :setting:`RETRY_TIMES` setting."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1015
msgid "RETRY_HTTP_CODES"
msgstr "RETRY_HTTP_CODES"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1017
msgid "Default: ``[500, 502, 503, 504, 522, 524, 408, 429]``"
msgstr "默认： ``[500、502、503、504、522、524、408、429]``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1019
msgid ""
"Which HTTP response codes to retry. Other errors (DNS lookup issues, "
"connections lost, etc) are always retried."
msgstr "要重试的HTTP响应码。其他错误 (DNS 查找问题、连接丢失等) 总是被检索。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1022
msgid ""
"In some cases you may want to add 400 to :setting:`RETRY_HTTP_CODES` because "
"it is a common code used to indicate server overload. It is not included by "
"default because HTTP specs say so."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1029
msgid "RETRY_EXCEPTIONS"
msgstr "RETRY_EXCEPTIONS"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1031
msgid "Default::"
msgstr "默认：:"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1033
msgid ""
"[\n"
"    'scrapy.exceptions.CannotResolveHostError',\n"
"    'scrapy.exceptions.DownloadConnectionRefusedError',\n"
"    'scrapy.exceptions.DownloadFailedError',\n"
"    'scrapy.exceptions.DownloadTimeoutError',\n"
"    'scrapy.exceptions.ResponseDataLossError',\n"
"    'twisted.internet.error.ConnectionDone',\n"
"    'twisted.internet.error.ConnectError',\n"
"    'twisted.internet.error.ConnectionLost',\n"
"    IOError,\n"
"    'scrapy.core.downloader.handlers.http11.TunnelError',\n"
"]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1046
msgid "List of exceptions to retry."
msgstr "需要重试的异常列表。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1048
msgid ""
"Each list entry may be an exception type or its import path as a string."
msgstr "每个列表条目可以是异常类型或导入路径作为字符串。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1050
msgid ""
"An exception will not be caught when the exception type is not in :setting:"
"`RETRY_EXCEPTIONS` or when the maximum number of retries for a request has "
"been exceeded (see :setting:`RETRY_TIMES`). To learn about uncaught "
"exception propagation, see :meth:`~scrapy.downloadermiddlewares."
"DownloaderMiddleware.process_exception`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1059
msgid "RETRY_PRIORITY_ADJUST"
msgstr "TRY_PRIORITY_ADJUST"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1061
msgid "Default: ``-1``"
msgstr "默认值： ``-1``"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1063
msgid "Adjust retry request priority relative to original request:"
msgstr "调整重试请求相对于原始请求的优先级："

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1065
