msgstr "积极的优先次序调整意味着更高的优先次序。"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1066
msgid "**a negative priority adjust (default) means lower priority.**"
msgstr "**负优先级调整 (默认) 意味着较低优先级。**"

#: ../../../topics/downloader-middleware.rst:1072
msgid "RobotsTxtMiddleware"
msgstr "机器人Txt中间件"

